    <p><b>About &lsquo;This Is Our Stop&rsquo;</b></p>
    <p>An experimental and open conversation space that connects people around familiar points across the region. Inspired by <a href="http://www.countablyinfinite.ca/">Karen Quinn Fung</a>&rsquo;s urban planning research, we hope to make city life more friendly and our transit infrastructure even better.<p>

